{"tid":101653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左年幾牛角，你問我答","createTime":"2017-01-31T04:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T15:00:09.000Z","uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6024ed33b4ca95d5100a58de482579cd46122f2e","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"都算係pt，但知得幾多嘢下"},{"pid":"76cbfccea2769fb406b5316b7fcdfe234e35f538","tid":101653,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"食過幾多條女"},{"pid":"31386f4e0bf7983872caa3de19013eb6bc68d694","tid":101653,"uid":18546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"係咪除左第一碟牛係好野 之後黎既牛都係垃圾？"},{"pid":"59c4ddbaf391db814d08391d2b784aaecfbe548f","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過幾多條女</blockquote><br />\n差唔多日日都返工咁濟，都冇機會食😪😪"},{"pid":"ab2edcb9042aa9947b0a2b4d66a405418ee96228","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪除左第一碟牛係好野 之後黎既牛都係垃圾？</blockquote><br />\n又唔係嘅，但有時會例外"},{"pid":"7aece4462480187f29d494e8a268d16a3ecdccea","tid":101653,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪除左第一碟牛係好野 之後黎既牛都係垃圾？</blockquote><br />\n又唔係嘅，但有時會例外</blockquote><br />\n第一碟開始係垃圾？"},{"pid":"61fcd327e1110e4f9f83d3b8ae54e62b3d97bcfc","tid":101653,"uid":65185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"d肉會唔會收返比第二枱客"},{"pid":"66f5e18ecba43c22fd14a0c0d5bb8d28c408428b","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪除左第一碟牛係好野 之後黎既牛都係垃圾？</blockquote><br />\n又唔係嘅，但有時會例外</blockquote><br />\n第一碟開始係垃圾？</blockquote><br />\n普遍都好嘅，但如果個客取消左就會出俾第二個客"},{"pid":"938a567066ee2879834f2153cbcf6e18c67454e2","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d肉會唔會收返比第二枱客</blockquote><br />\n食過一定唔會，但未食過就有啲可能"},{"pid":"a50ddc4616aca764984083f1f746dab1ea58311e","tid":101653,"uid":66058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"好鍾意食<br />\n但有冇黑暗野？"},{"pid":"9416ca763984b3260a73ec78f524201dff0ced07","tid":101653,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96e641e0e240d0d6cab0c195df3240fcb4831b5a","tid":101653,"uid":28729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"任食㗎喎"},{"pid":"6adc5a0c5460795a625f6fd7eec9b647c4de1e04","tid":101653,"uid":65185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"係果度返工係咪可以任吃靚牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079478b8826011cb631a164bd70c6f911b115dc1","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意食<br />\n但有冇黑暗野？</blockquote><br />\n正常每走完一枱要換個網，因為會有油同污糟，但可能上個客燒完甜品見個網冇油漬就唔換。<br />\n公筷個人覺得唔係幾衛生"},{"pid":"d0fcb6a7c885744be85d3a8570dd213faca80f0a","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係果度返工係咪可以任吃靚牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，但有啲石鍋類同拉麵如果個客取消同冇單就可以。<br />\n牛角飯同溫泉玉子飯可以任食"},{"pid":"9ede88676d50a0cffe0a73a9d23192b09b40e422","tid":101653,"uid":64775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"勁鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb5577e8144f21498747fdfb4457e9c7e928b95","tid":101653,"uid":65185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"上網睇人講日本，台灣牛角係全部有放題<br />\n點解香港限死得幾間仲要9：30後先有<br />\n<br />\n放題真係抵好多，試過一個人吃差唔多400$都唔飽，放題250$可以任屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adfefa932ede8e29af60b5580aa45bbb70ab7ff","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網睇人講日本，台灣牛角係全部有放題<br />\n點解香港限死得幾間仲要9：30後先有<br />\n<br />\n放題真係抵好多，試過一個人吃差唔多400$都唔飽，放題250$可以任屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有冇巴絲發覺牛角開啲舖越來越細。細舖冇得做放題，所以先局住係某啲舖做放題同要啲人嗌下Grand Menu先balence到生意額"},{"pid":"1d191b6558e7ccd6cc0ab10c867e5f7d9024ffe2","tid":101653,"uid":65185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係果度返工係咪可以任吃靚牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，但有啲石鍋類同拉麵如果個客取消同冇單就可以。<br />\n牛角飯同溫泉玉子飯可以任食</blockquote><br />\n會唔會講個客吃剩，例如半碟/大半碟，望落去幹淨果d收埋，收工吃？<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得呢d肉就噤掉好浪費，自己出去買都唔平"},{"pid":"f5e082863a76ccdff4717ae419312c37bf5a181b","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無任食嗰陣食過<br />\n又貴又唔好食</blockquote><br />\n其實我都覺有啲貴"},{"pid":"ae31ae1848109fd2562645b7348e5bafe2790669","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係果度返工係咪可以任吃靚牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，但有啲石鍋類同拉麵如果個客取消同冇單就可以。<br />\n牛角飯同溫泉玉子飯可以任食</blockquote><br />\n會唔會講個客吃剩，例如半碟/大半碟，望落去幹淨果d收埋，收工吃？<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得呢d肉就噤掉好浪費，自己出去買都唔平</blockquote><br />\n緊係唔會，俾著係你都唔會食，因為你都唔知個客有冇吐口水落碟肉度，同埋基本上唔會有食半碟肉嘅情況出現，因為四十幾蚊得果幾塊肉"},{"pid":"0d554b6bc799dec2d5d0b7951fc2af1915d3785b","tid":101653,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"依家仲有無下午茶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ebe21ca858498dd64270f28a7e6caf7728c247","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家仲有無下午茶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇"},{"pid":"cfbe906e557b7fb8d4fd9137da0d2c869392bc44","tid":101653,"uid":71881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"f4255b2bc16802d8405a326c5be296251194c832","tid":101653,"uid":44153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"屌，諗撚錯<br />\n仲想屌你鳩up自己做牛角，不如話自己做過牛歡喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}